{"type":"message","id":"7c33fa3a","parentId":"0d44f1d3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:23:34.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing stock performance**\n\nI see that the moving averages are below 20, and the price of 81.96 is below the MA10, 20, 60, and 120 but above the MA5. This suggests a weak rebound. The year-to-date performance is down 6.6%, with a considerable distance from the high at 36%. There seems to be a mix of steady revenue growth but negative operating cash flow year-to-date. I should potentially mention whether it’s suitable to buy now, even if the user didn't specifically ask.\n\n**Assessing buy strategy**\n\nI think I can provide a deep analysis of the current position. It seems to be better than some alternatives in terms of certainty, but the current chart doesn't support an immediate heavy buy. It might be wise to wait for stabilization at 85 or 88, or a drop to 79 without breaking. Since earlier they asked about buying, I could mention trading perspectives in my response to address their interests comprehensively.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_01c730309d5123030169c5f800a240819b97e3e1b5a4651959\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxfgOdylNUmJHIOmFA5jl-1f37_Ya23c9KLrMs7sockXGF1HEeUztme_7G_gH2tJtv5SCNuUJq0SqXKS4QeL7BZZOfgqZcU0jVxUNxeMOqw-pDZ6QpG-5EgokunzlP92zzkVgoJqaAoUyGCmlGiuD94CepTGtOhiLwH4lxjPcOSsevGvW1OzFxZhAwcva4U4U8qH5535FtcacdK6S2RPnuPW7ExfWAD5C_PtqDvpWOlbow1lENlafPejx1GRVU5bSm8nDGy_pPWHnFXNjkMDscS6zSKTDDZPmeSEwQ1muUnJb2zlxPDr81ny5hYeHutcRFuYXAdvub0iWBoE_koprJztLXPiieZ6zbtkSeJE1zLy82wTHI1FHQ3GfBtyqWBy013AGuOdf26kzc4r5A-jQk7v_cAwYkoinWwWnS4Ih3BqEkOMp8UlQD5AnOvF1zI5SuOMFRs5veC6mfTY8s5UB4bw7CDGciaSYncRxxZjzCToj5X8YdwOdfc4IO2-D5DyrMU-fx7vSPhUukw1zUdAiNZRQOwaC6luh4LBf6kxm0kqseGCd0wtOxGIYwCHhFgcmkLReCZAfcYqW_DRGXEcBtSMT4xZ_PaEgN9QWOgKU-9mnGkvNU_X9W2uXD3OD-B-wpJ1jfrMkxXagW1fjSouu6ATWMbUH-vZ8DkmVNx8BHmQWDN5d_DmrOy33-kOiEwkQ--PownIeWXU1BFwEyQnFnqOy-w4WLWZaAYj3b4iMi4JnqCN6UAS7o