{"type":"message","id":"db0cf7fa","parentId":"22d99ef1","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:26:01.431Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering stock recommendations**\n\nI think we can rank five tickets across different dimensions for users holding 利通. I need to keep in mind that non-trading time constraints don’t apply since it’s trading day. But I should avoid giving executable buy prices. The agents emphasize checking real-time market conditions and individual confirmations first. I checked market breadth earlier, and it should still be relevant now. It’s essential to have today’s market status and stock confirmations before giving any buy recommendations or priorities.\n\n**Framing stock priority recommendations**\n\nI should probably avoid giving explicit buy recommendations and instead frame it as \"观察优先级\" rather than \"买入优先级,\" because I’m missing some real-time data. The user wants a total sort, so I can say it's under the current perspective or portfolio management. I might mention that my ranking is based on the latest available data, and it isn't immediate buy advice due to fluctuations in real-time stock confirmations. Updating the ACTIVE_TASK could be a good idea too!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_01c730309d5123030169c5f89cabd0819bbf735a0830f8af5f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxfirwzU6WSH4eiAU8KX6h_WImvtzMwIWtLlCLMmbgM33gijjDEVyzDLjawM2wnpK2LYfrITfvQYV8LiQLYz8_CsXdqnr8jkCkDFG8n4BozIAf5XnPpql2EOFSNJtVbKyWiWSX1Y-KLYUZPo3n-j9PWljzrTChbkSGJ8UiOLYXpUO2PYUhXZ2xs15RZAQNouz5H0yhGnFTmmMXSkP0bUNDp9FwGNfpaGS0s-QsYfp_IJCHscDjN7weQyyK-i4Pr0fA7yLZ_DdtBQUu7cTPU2_guULUMu8ZHiG_ClgC5pVWg9l6Q8d9xgNgGWUMZNVYZpxxmmsTPiv4_j4wHNsF5hL8JiHZW02jD4Q-a3ZFMdQ9TQVI0Y03RnwqAQNBnmy1YOEbvKqGlJQHXY9lpkrfr3__81L2bem9trc7phPZTVZnlJ1cKEo9WTaWBFKJpibgoMnWpdtTmsSGDvnRCEzkBiPpLA25mxyiMYvUNdKVUU5abosX3KflgBWbEeNNC4eQJkc9mY-Yr-iXt_4l0fdeReRasEs2OfwAjGkDNkQWKCmhKBQ0-5bWlxc-IP2WhMBxjqvch8c0Kf-YhCUAyJdd70PESNAoBUA3YrPFH6vdT9wNq